-- Lions Gate Entertainment to Work With Icahn on Acquisition Opportunities
-- Greg Chang
-- 2010-07-09T21:22:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/lions-gate-entertainment-to-work-with-icahn-on-acquisition-opportunities.html

          
          
             Lions Gate Entertainment Corp. said
it agreed to work with Carl C. Icahn on certain acquisition
opportunities beginning today and ending on July 19. Lions Gate
agreed to refrain from specified actions during that period,
including encouraging any other people to buy Lions Gate
securities outside of normal business.    
          
          


  


        